{"tid":2165681,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求問] HSBC recruitment","createTime":"2020-08-20T03:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:45:01.000Z","uid":360155,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2ee625d481889578ac18bd3dd3686c2ce7f12fd4","tid":2165681,"uid":360155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"想問佢地個recruitment process係咪都好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網見到有人講過可能會process到最後不了了之左<br />\n<br />\n大約兩星期前申請左個position<br />\n即日(星期五)仲收到通知做online test<br />\n隔兩日(星期一)我做左<br />\n第二日status就update左做passed<br />\n又隔多兩日(星期四)HR打黎phone interview 一切正常<br />\n佢話會pass CV俾senior management再process<br />\n到依家一個禮拜 冇聲冇氣<br />\n我有check住application status<br />\n一直都係&rdquo;online assessment passed&rdquo;<br />\n直到今日轉左&rdquo;required online assessment(s) passed&rdquo; <br />\n想問有冇人試過同樣情況？兩者有分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪到呢個stage就止步了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2425f90ad1db609ed1148520fa3851c2fe7e92","tid":2165681,"uid":2357,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"放棄啦，無左啦，搵第份"},{"pid":"f68f6c156350fa4939880db5d6360ddad28bc13d","tid":2165681,"uid":360155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f2425f90ad1db609ed1148520fa3851c2fe7e92","tid":2165681,"uid":2357,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"放棄啦，無左啦，搵第份"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"遇過同樣情況？"},{"pid":"15bb9050a43aa7e653db822ab98db50e45d60194","tid":2165681,"uid":319953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T05:31:55.000Z","msg":"都好睇你咩division <br />\n之前做過本